pma:database.name: 2110_ranking
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `event_rank` ( `rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `rank2` int(11) NOT NULL, `card_id` text NOT NULL, `player_name` text NOT NULL, `score_i1` int(11) NOT NULL, `score_bi1` int(11) NOT NULL, `last_play_tenpo_id` text NOT NULL, `fcol1` int(99) NOT NULL, `fcol2` int(99) NOT NULL, `tenpo_name` text NOT NULL, `pref_id` text NOT NULL, `pref` text NOT NULL, `area_id` text NOT NULL, `area` text NOT NULL, `title` text NOT NULL, `org_rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `org_rank2` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`rank`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `global` ( `rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `rank2` int(11) NOT NULL, `card_id` text NOT NULL, `player_name` text NOT NULL, `score_i1` int(11) NOT NULL, `score_bi1` int(11) NOT NULL, `last_play_tenpo_id` text NOT NULL, `fcol1` int(99) NOT NULL, `fcol2` int(99) NOT NULL, `tenpo_name` text NOT NULL, `pref_id` text NOT NULL, `pref` text NOT NULL, `area_id` text NOT NULL, `area` text NOT NULL, `title` text NOT NULL, `org_rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `org_rank2` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`rank`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `play_num_rank` ( `rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `rank2` int(11) NOT NULL, `pcol1` text NOT NULL, `score_bi1` int(11) NOT NULL, `title` text NOT NULL, `artist` text NOT NULL, `org_rank` int(11) NOT NULL, `org_rank2` int(11) NOT NULL ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
